cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a novel deep learning algorithm for Active Inference, which is a theory of action arising from neuroscience. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also deals with robotics and control tasks, which suggests the sub-categories cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as possible options.
